THE GAME
--------

  'Pathos' is a Workbench game based on the well known 'sliding-
tiles' concept. The idea is to move tiles that have parts of
'paths' on them, so they create a path between the entry, located
at the top, to the exit, which is located at the bottom of the
game board.

  Pathos keeps in memory the number of tiles that were used to
create the longest and shortest path since the game was run...

  Have fun!

